title: Tillerson raises prospect of Venezuela military ouster of Maduro
text:
Tillerson raises prospect of Venezuela military ouster of Maduro Thursday, February 01, 2018 - 01:08 
U.S. Secretary of State Rex Tillerson on Thursday raised the prospect that the Venezuelan military could decide to oust President Nicolas Maduro but said he did not know whether that would happen. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
